        - PERMISSION_DENIED
        - TASK_NOT_FOUND
        - TASK_NOT_REGISTERED
        - TASK_DISABLED
        - QUERY_PARAMS_TOO_LARGE
        - IDEMPOTENCY_CONFLICT
        - INVALID_TASK_STATE
        - FILE_EXPIRED
        - FILE_NOT_READY
        - FILE_VERIFY_ERROR
        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID
        - DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE
